# Relationship Growth Partner — Cursor Rules
# Muhammad Harist · June 2026

## Project
Web app private untuk Harist dan Dian. AI-powered journaling dan
relationship growth tool. Engine: Claude Sonnet 4.6 via Anthropic API.

## Stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript — strict mode ON
- Tailwind CSS — utility-first, no custom CSS kecuali terpaksa
- Supabase — PostgreSQL + Auth (atau PIN sederhana untuk MVP)
- html2pdf.js — client-side PDF export
- Vercel — deployment

## Folder convention
app/harist/     → Harist's space (dashboard + chat)
app/dian/       → Dian's space (dashboard + chat)
app/growth/     → Shared growth dashboard
app/api/chat/   → Claude API streaming handler
lib/prompts.ts  → Semua system prompts (jangan taruh di component)
lib/storage.ts  → Supabase CRUD helpers
lib/supabase.ts → Supabase client
types/index.ts  → Semua TypeScript types
components/     → Shared UI components

## Code style
- Selalu pakai TypeScript types dari types/index.ts
- Functional components only, no class components
- use client directive hanya kalau butuh interactivity
- Error handling wajib di semua fetch/async call
- Loading state wajib di semua async UI
- Jangan hardcode string — gunakan constants atau types

## UI / UX — Color Palette
- Primary green: #074836 (rgp-green)
- Accent yellow: #FFD700 (rgp-yellow)
- Background cream: #F9F7F2 (rgp-cream)
- Harist accent: #7C3AED (rgp-harist)
- Dian accent: #0F766E (rgp-dian)
- Mobile-first responsive
- Rounded corners (rounded-3xl, pill buttons)

## Claude API
- Model: claude-sonnet-4-6
- Max tokens: 2048 per response
- Always streaming
- System prompt dari lib/prompts.ts
- API key dari env: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY

## Security
- ANTHROPIC_API_KEY hanya di server-side
- PIN auth: PIN_HARIST, PIN_DIAN
